Package etomica.data

Class DataSourceTensorVirialHard

  • java.lang.Object
    • etomica.data.DataSourceTensorVirialHard
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IDataSource, IntegratorHard.CollisionListener, java.io.Serializable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    DataSourceTensorVirialHardProfile

    public class DataSourceTensorVirialHard
extends java.lang.Object
implements IDataSource, IntegratorHard.CollisionListener, java.io.Serializable
    A MeterTensor that returns the virial component of the pressure tensor for a hard potential. This is the counterpart to MeterVelocityTensor, also called by the surface tension meter.
